open_houses.description: This Hollywood Regency mid-century style home is ideally situated at the end of a quiet cul de sac, and sits on an expansive 11,000 sq. ft. lot. Tasteful free flowing floorplan steps down into a spacious living room and boasts beautiful Italian tile that Looks like wood throughout much of the home. Cozy den includes a wet bar with granite countertops and a gas burning fireplace. Chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances, includes double oven, gas stovetop and an island countertop that separates a generously sized breakfast nook. There is plentiful custom cabinetry throughout the house. Enjoy the serenity of the entertainer's back yard, with a huge covered patio, BBQ island, designer pool and spa with water features, and even more patio areas that wrap around the house. Large side yard with fruit trees which could be used as a dog run. Other amenities and upgrades include a central vacuum system, new five ton HVAC, two water heaters and a completely remodeled master bath

Updated 3 Story Townhouse in Valley Glen! Charming kitchen. Laminate flooring. Bonus space perfect for home office. Laundry inside unit. Renovations include kitchen, floors, recessed lighting, deck & paint--plus oven, dishwasher & water heater. This is 1 of 3 units with direct access (from the living room) to a great backyard-style outdoor space. Unit #1 just sold off market for $580,000 (not in the MLS) on June 17, 2022; info is available in the public record.

1st time on the market since 1962. This original owner's Mulholland close classic Mid-Century modern view home is truly the one you have been waiting for. Located near the top of the coveted Stone Hills in Sherman Oaks, this ideal home is surrounded by period landscape & a variety of abundant fruit trees. Front door opens to reveal a refreshed floor plan w/engineered wd floors in most rms. The step-down great rm w/vaulted wd beamed ceiling is anchored by a frplc & your eye is drawn immediately to the viewing deck overlooking the Valley lights & mountains beyond. The open family & dining areas are adj to the recently updated kit, including a double oven w/1 convection oven. This wing of the home opens to a low maintenance yet expansive & pvt patio/yard perfect for entertaining. Walls of glass in all rooms truly bring the outdoors in & showcase garden greenery & the magnificent views. Westside close & in the highly desired Dixie Cyn School district, this home awaits its next lucky owner.

WONDERFUL & WARM TRADITIONAL GEM IN PRIME LOS FELIZ HILLS! This is a RARE OPPORTUNITY & PRICE for many reasons! (Home is beautifully surrounded by green lush nature & also, It is the only active listing North of Los Feliz Blvd currently under $2.8 million). Great chance to get into this coveted estate neighborhood with grand trophy homes all around. Verdant new landscape design, abounding with character, and offering wonderful hillside views on it almost 7,500 sq ft lot. This SECRET pocket of Griffith Park Blvd is all residential and has a cozy, quaint neighborhood feel - and at the top of the street: a lovely Cul-de-Sac! (with DIRECT PRIVATE ACCESS TO GRIFFITH PARK hiking trails + bike paths + pony rides + children train ride + Tregnan Golf Academy).

From the moment you step into this classic Hollywood Spanish-style villa, you will feel warmed and welcomed by its arched doorways, hardwood floors, and sunlit windows offering spectacular views over the neighboring hills, with their lush trees and tiled rooftops. An expansive and welcoming kitchen is adjacent to a charming dining room with access to an outdoor deck with grill which is perfect for entertaining inside and out, surrounded by palms and flowers. The open living room has sliding doors to a romantic private patio, and three rooms: a den/study with a high ceiling, vintage tile and decorative fireplace, a cozy but ample bedroom, and a full bathroom with tub and shower complete the main level. This is a home that provides solace, serenity and sunshine.
